<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Your Order Has Been Created</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; color: #333;">
  <div style="margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>

    <p>Thank you for your order at <strong>{{website}}</strong>.</p>

    <p>Here are the details of your order:</p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{orderId}}</li>
      <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{customerName}}</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{customerEmail}}</li>
      <li><strong>Phone:</strong> {{customerPhone}}</li>
      <li><strong>Address:</strong> {{customerAddress}}</li>
      <li><strong>Note:</strong> {{note}}</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Order Items:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      {{#each items}}
        <li>{{serviceName}} - Quantity: {{quantity}} - Price: ${{price}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <p>We will notify you once your order status changes.</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 40px;">Best regards,<br/>The <strong>{{website}}</strong> Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
